<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>278</hymn_number>
<key>D</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Vai-lamtah ralkap ka si maw? Bawipa hnu ka zul maw? A-mah riantuan ka
 tih lai lo, A min tha ka thanh lai.

[C1]
   Min ah cun (Min ah cun) min sung a si (min sung a si) Kei ca a thimi
   cu (Kei ca a thimi cu) Vai-lamtahnak ka put ca-ah, Sui luchin ka hmuh lai.

[V2]
 Midang laksawng hmuhter awkah, Ka thih tiang ka tuan lai, Vancung
 phakter tu ka si lai, Minmei cung khua tha ah.

[C2]
   Min ah cun (Min ah cun) min sung a si (min sung a si) Kei ca a thimi
   cu (Kei ca a thimi cu) Vai-lamtahnak ka put ca-ah, Sui luchin ka hmuh lai.

[V3]
 Raldoh awk ral kha an um maw? Tilian tihnung chungah, Vawlei chaw nih
 Pathian sinah, A ka phakter lai maw?

[C3]
   Min ah cun (Min ah cun) min sung a si (min sung a si) Kei ca a thimi
   cu (Kei ca a thimi cu) Vai-lamtahnak ka put ca-ah, Sui luchin ka hmuh lai.

[V4]
 Mi ngan si awkah kaa zuam lai, Bawipa ral ka thatter, Na rian ca sifah
 ka in lai, Nangmah bawmhnak ka herh.

[C4]
   Min ah cun (Min ah cun) min sung a si (min sung a si) Kei ca a thimi
   cu (Kei ca a thimi cu) Vai-lamtahnak ka put ca-ah, Sui luchin ka hmuh lai.</lyrics>
<title>VAILAMTAH RALKAP CH278</title>
</song>